  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，伙计，我有个重要的事情要告诉你，仔细听好了，别被什么鸟儿分散了注意力。那个叫Ref的家伙偷了我的货，你应该还记得吧？猜怎么着，我找到了他藏部分货物的线索，不知道他到底想干嘛，也许是在等买家来取货，也许不是，谁知道呢。\n\n总之，我需要有人找到那个地方，告诉我货物是否还在那儿，我可能会派人去查看，说不定能趁买家不备抓住他，撬点情报出来？哦，我是说礼貌地向他询问案件细节。\n\n我相信地点就在海关区的三号和四号仓库附近，我想你以前自己也查看过那个区域，对吧？你对那儿很熟，所以何不去瞅瞅呢？",
    "en": "Yo, lad, I got something for you, it's important so take a listen, and don't get distracted by some birds. This Ref guy stole some of my goods, you remember that I suppose, well guess what, I got a lead on where he hid some of the cargo, no idea what he wants with them, perhaps this is like a deal or something and he is waiting for his buyer to pick it up, perhaps not, who knows.\n\nAnyway, I need someone to find the place, tell me if the cargo is there or not, I might send over someone to check it out, maybe we can catch the buyer off guard and squeeze some information out of him? Oh I meant to politely ask him for details on this case.\n\nI believe it's close to warehouse three and four in the customs zone, I think you once checked out the zone yourself, right? You're familiar with that place so why don't you take a gander."
  },
